.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, soy-milk, sprite
There 4 different types of food: cherry, watermelon, plum, onion
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, weightlifting, basketball, skateboarding
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, malaysian, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, train
 1. the german is between the person eating plum and the person driving the bike##2
 2. the pakistani is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 3. the person eating onion is on the left of the canadian##1
 4. the german is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person driving the ship##2
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person watching action movies and the person eating onion##2
 9. the person watching thriller movies is the person eating onion##1
10. the person eating cherry is on the far left##1
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
13. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
14. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | fanta       | soy-milk   | almond-milk |
| Food         | cherry     | plum   | onion    | watermelon  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel | thriller   | western     |
| Sport   | skateboarding    | volleyball       | weightlifting | basketball        |
| Nationality   | pakistani | malaysian   | german     | canadian    |
| Transport     | bus       | ship        | train      | bike        |

