There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, egyptian, mexican, russian
4 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, poker, monopoly
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, soccer, weightlifting
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, skateboard, subway, van
 1. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 2. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the russian##1
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the mexican and the person drinking tea##2
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is between the person driving the van and the person playing scrabble##2
10. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
11. the person drinking tea is the person driving the subway##1
12. the person who's birthday is in february is the person driving the skateboard##1
13. the person playing poker is between the person who's birthday is in april and the egyptian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |       3       |    4     |
