The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, family, scientific
There are 4 different nationalities: american, french, malaysian, russian
There 4 different types of food: lime, lemon, pomegranate, orange
 1. the chaman-smoker is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the malaysian##2
 2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the designer##1
 3. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 4. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 6. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
 7. the scientist is on the left of the american##1
 8. the person eating pomegranate is the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person eating lime is between the scientist and the person who's hobby is limed-games##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is limed-games is on the left of the person eating lime##1
12. the software-developer is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
13. the pall-mall-smoker is the pall-mall-smoker##1
14. the person who's hobby is gardening is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
