 4. the person watching superhero movies is between the owner of the fish and the person watching spy movies##2
 5. the argentine is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the owner of the fish is on the right of the colonial house##1
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
 8. the tower house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
11. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the modern house##1
12. the colombian is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the argentine##1

