.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, radish, strawberry, zucchini
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, firefighter, musician, security-guard
4 different games are played: bridge, domino, monopoly, go
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, soccer, swimming, volleyball
4 different pets are kept: frog, mouse, rat, turtle
 1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the musician##1
 5. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing go is between the analyst and the person eating zucchini##2
 7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person eating blueberry##1
10. the firefighter is the owner of the turtle##1
11. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
12. the person drinking fanta is the owner of the rat##1
13. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda        | milk     | cola        | fanta    |
| Food          | strawberry     | radish   | blueberry   | zucchini |
| Job           | security-guard | analyst  | firefighter | musician |
| Game   | domino            | monopoly    | go        | bridge  |
| Sport   | swimming          | biathlon | volleyball      | soccer  |
| Pet           | mouse          | frog     | turtle      | rat      |

