.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda, tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, azalea, marigold, dahlia
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, freelancer, pilot, security-guard
4 different games are played: snooker, canasta, backgammon, whist
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, german, nigerian
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, hamster, hedgehog
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the pilot##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the chef is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 7. the person playing whist is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 8. the person who growsdahlia is between the american and the owner of the goldfish##2
 9. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
10. the nigerian is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
11. the owner of the ferret is the security-guard##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
13. the person playing snooker is between the chef and the owner of the ferret##2
14. the security-guard is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |       3        |     4     |
| Beverage      | tea      | hot-chocolate | lemonade       | mirinda   |
| Flower          | azalea   | marigold          | dahlia           | rose |
| Job           | chef     | freelancer    | security-guard | pilot     |
| Game   | whist   | snooker          | canasta         | backgammon     |
| Nationality   | dutch    | american      | nigerian       | german    |
| Pet           | hedgehog | hamster       | ferret         | goldfish  |

