.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda, tea, water
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, grapefruit, lime, peach
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, photography, puzzles, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, may, january, july
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bluemaster, bongani, blend
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, pakistani, russian, thai
 1. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
 3. the mexican is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 5. the person eating lime is on the right of the pakistani##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is the prince-smoker##1
 9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the russian##1
10. the person eating peach is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
12. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person drinking water and the person who's birthday is in january##2
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage      | mirinda | tea         | water       | fanta         |
| Food          | cabbage | grapefruit  | lime        | peach         |
| Hobby         | puzzles | photography | cooking     | woodworking   |
| Birthday           | january | march  | may | july |
| Cigar   | bongani  | blend     | bluemaster       | prince   |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani   | thai        | mexican       |

