.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, mirinda, sprite
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, eggplant, pepper, pumpkin
4 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse, snake, lizard
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, dutch, egyptian, french
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, sailing, tennis
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, lawyer, coach, nurse
 1. the person eating pepper is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
 3. the canadian is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
 4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the french is the person eating eggplant##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is the engineer##1
 8. the lawyer is the person eating pumpkin##1
 9. the dutch is the nurse##1
10. the french is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person drinking iced-tea and the owner of the ferret##2
12. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
13. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | sprite     | mirinda  | iced-tea |
| Food          | artichoke     | pepper     | eggplant | pumpkin  |
| Pet         | lizard   | ferret | mouse  | snake   |
| Nationality   | dutch         | egyptian   | french   | canadian |
| Sport         | cricket       | sailing    | tennis   | climbing |
| Job     | nurse        | engineer   | coach   | lawyer      |

 